column8: Bouldy and I, we're proud to be of service, Your Highness!
Something I can do for you?
Let's get you on your way!
I interest you in one of these?
Think I can be of service!
Go on and take your pick!
What can I do for you?
That who I think it is...?
Could use a little help here...!
Hey lend a hand would you?
I'm in a bit of trouble Prince...!
Could use a hand I think...!
Mind lending me a hand here?
Hate to bother you, but, uh...
Just in the nick of time!
Am I glad you showed up.

Hoh that is quite an undertaking, Prince. If it wasn't you yourself proposing it, I'd like to call it madness, truth be told. Though you're just mad enough to pull it off! Hey, hold a moment, here -- I've got something could be of some help.
All right, Prince Z., if you're to be so generous with me, I wanted to make sure that I could get you back. Not centuries from now, but right away. So, take this, with my compliments.
Ohh, now this is going to get me through at least another century of boulder-pushing I should say! And I have got something for you as well.
Caught me on a break again!
How nice to see you, Prince!
Think I can do that, Prince!
Got that right here, Prince Z.!
Oh, please, have mercy and all that!
That your best shot, Prince Z.?
Now don't get frustrated all right?
You getting ready for the road ahead?
Wow you are strong Prince Z.!
Do tell the Furies I said hi!
May you get out of here this time, Highness!
Think he'll go all the way this time, Bouldy?
Pick on somebody your own size, Prince!
That's one fight you aren't going to win!
Takes more than that to budge old Bouldy, Prince!
Bouldy can take whatever you dish out!
Now there's no need for that here, Prince.
Try all you like, there, Prince!
Hey that's my friend, Prince Z.
That's one tough rock you're messing with.
Oh what did Bouldy ever do to you?
Let's get the drop on her!
Why if it isn't Master Thanatos!
What good would that do here?
Call us when you need us!
Thanks on behalf of Bouldy there!
That's one good rock, isn't he, Prince!
Your offering has been accepted, Prince!
That's good of you, Prince Z.!
Think Bouldy's warming up to you!
Bouldy's a good listener isn't he!
You have been blessed by Bouldy!
Thank you for picking up a bit!
Break all the pots you like!
Oh those shades aren't so bad.
No need for that here, Prince.
They'll just come back next time.
Those shades are stuck here, Prince.
Oh, I'll just stash that one away, then, Prince!
Is that for me, Prince Z.? Well then, all right!
I'll take that off your hands if you insist, Highness.
I've not much need of that, but I can take it, Prince!
Come now, Highness, you really shouldn't have.
Please don't take this the wrong way, Prince, but I cannot accept something like this.
Apologies, Prince Z., but I've no need of that. You'd best hang onto it.
Afraid I have no need for that, Highness, though I appreciate the gesture there!
Thank you, Prince Z., though I've no use for this right now.
Your Highness, I was wondering if you might hear me out.
Prince Z., I've a small favor I would ask of you if you don't mind.
Wanted to ask you something here, Highness.
Quick request if you've a moment for us, Prince.
Ohh, this is the choicest stuff that you've procured, Prince Z.!
Is that for me really, Highness? You know I absolutely love the stuff?
Augh, look at what the Prince has brought for us, Bouldy!
On behalf of Bouldy and myself, we're very grateful for your gesture here.
Oh, look how happy Bouldy is!
You two have a real thing going!
